---
source: src/highlighting/highlighter.rs
expression: "cfg.highlight(\"~/foo/a.sh && ~/foo/b.sh\")?\n.to_string().replace(cfg.homedir.path().to_str().unwrap(), \"<HOME>\")"
---
~/foo/a.sh && ~/foo/b.sh

0   10  `~/foo/a.sh`  CALLABLE `<HOME>/foo/a.sh`
11  13  `&&`          keyword.operator.logical.and
14  24  `~/foo/b.sh`  CALLABLE `<HOME>/foo/b.sh`
